<div id="content" class="backgrnd4"><div id="right"><div id="box6"><h2 class="backgrnd12"><span class="text1">Proceedings of the First Annual Conference on Innovative Applications of Artificial Intelligence</span></h2><div class="content"><p><i>Sponsored by the Association for the Advancement of Artificial Intelligence</i></p><p><b>Edited by Herb Schorr and Alain Rappaport</b></p><p>March 28&ndash;30, 1989, Stanford, California . Published by The AAAI Press, Menlo Park, California. <a href="../../Press/Proceedings/iaai89.php">This proceedings is available in book and CD format.</a></p><p><b>Please Note:</b> Abstracts are linked to individual titles, and will appear in a separate browser window. Full-text versions of the papers are linked to the abstract text. Access to full text may be restricted to AAAI members. PDF file sizes may be large!</p><hr /><p class="left">Contributors</p> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-000.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Preface</a><br /><i>Herbert Schorr and Alain Rappaport</i></p><br /> <h3 class="left">Aerospace</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-001.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Applicationsof Artificial Intelligence to Space Shuttle Mission Control</a><br /><i> John F. Muratore, Troy A. Heindel, Terri B. Murphy, Arthur N. Rasmussen, and Robert Z. McFarland</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-002.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">An IntelligentTraining System for Space Shuttle Flight Controllers</a><br /><i> R. BowenLoftin, Lui Wang, Paul Baffes, and Grace Hua</i></p><h3 class="left">Banking and Finance</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-003.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Analyst</a><br /><i>Michael A. Hutson</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-004.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Innovation andAI in the World of Financial Trading</a><br /><i> Elizabeth Byrnes, Thomas Campfield, and Bruce Connor</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-005.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">TheIntelligent Banking System</a><br /><i> Kenan Sahin and Keith Sawyer</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-029.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">AMTS Automated Money Transfer Service (AMTS)</a><br /><i> Ashim K. Das</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-030.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The Authorizer&rsquo;s Assistant: A Knowledge-Based Credit Authorization System for American Express</a><br /><i> James M. Dzierzanowski, Kenneth R. Chrisman, Gary J. MacKinnon, and Philip Klahr</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-006.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">PFPS--Personal Financial Planning System</a><br /><i>Kyle W. Kindle, Ross S. Cann, Michael R. Craig, and Thomas J. Martin</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-007.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Application-Driven Architecture: A Case Study of Syntel</a><br /><i>Peter E. Hart</i></p><h3 class="left">Biotechology</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-008.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The PepProPeptide Synthesis Expert System</a><br /><i> Matt Heffron, Philip R. Martz, Suresh Kalbag, Douglas F. Dyckes, and Paul Voelker</i></p><h3 class="left">Emergency Services</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-009.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">AKnowledge-Based Emergency Control Advisory System</a><br /><i> John Aubrey and Zoltan Nemes-Nemeth</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-010.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">MannTall--ARescue Operations Assistant</a><br /><i> Martin Brooks, Steinar Carlsen,and Atle Honne</i></p><h3 class="left">Law</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-011.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">An ExpertSystem for Legal Consultation</a><br /><i> Paul Clancy, Gerald Hoenig, andArnold Schmitt</i></p><h3 class="left">Manufacturing Assembly</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-012.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Can Build -- AState of the Need Application</a><br /><i> Robin M. Krumholz</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-013.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Charley: AnExpert System for Diagnostics of Manufacturing Equipment</a><br /><i> AtulBajpai and Richard Marczewski</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-014.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">HarnessingDetailed Assembly Process Knowledge</a><br /><i> William J. McClay and John A. Thompson</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-015.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Knowledge-BasedStatistical Process Control</a><br /><i> Kenneth R. Anderson, David E.Coleman, C. Ray Hill, Andrew P. Jaworski, Patrick L. Love, Douglas A.Spindler, and Marwan Simaan</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-016.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">LogisticsManagement System (LMS)</a><br /><i> Gerald Sullivan and Kenneth Fordyce</i></p><h3 class="left">Manufacturing Design</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-017.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Coolsys: ACooling Systems Design Assistant</a><br /><i> Patricia G. Friel, Richard J. Mayer, and Jeffrey C. Lockledge</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-018.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">DesignAdvisor: A Knowledge-Based IC Design Critic</a><br /><i> Robin L. Steele,Scott A. Richardson, and Michael A. Winchell</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-019.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">OHCS:Hydraulic Circuit Design Assistant</a><br /><i> Yusei Nakashima and Tomio Baba</i></p><h3 class="left">Media</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-020.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Times: AnExpert System for Media Planning</a><br /><i> George Girod, Patrice Orgeasand Patrick Landry</i></p><h3 class="left">Military</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-021.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">MACPlan: AMixed Initiative Approach to Airlift Planning</a><br /><i> Kirsten Y. Kissmeyer and Anne M. Tallant</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-022.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Naval BattleManagement Decision Aiding</a><br /><i> Ted E. Senator, T. M. Witte, andTheodore Kral</i></p><h3 class="left">Music</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-023.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Wolfgang: GoalFormulation with Emotional Constraints -- Musical Composition byEmotional Computation</a><br /><i> R. Douglas Riecken</i></p><h3 class="left">Operations Management</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-028.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Enhanced System Monitor (ESM)</a><br /><i> John E. Girard</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-024.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">ExpertOperator: Deploying YES/MVS II</a><br /><i> R. A. Chekaluk, E. M. Hufziger, A. J. Finkel, K. R. Milliken, and N. B. Waite</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-025.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Planning theDischarging and Loading of Container Ships</a><br /><i> Tat-Leong Chew, Andrew Gill, and Joo-Hong Lim</i></p><h3 class="left">Personal Management</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-026.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The Ford MotorCompany Direct Labor Management System</a><br /><i> John O'Brien, Henry Brice, Schott Hatfield, Wayne P. Johnson, and Richard Woodhead</i></p><h3 class="left">Retail Packaging</h3> <p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/1989/iaai89-027.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">PackagingAdvisor: An Expert System for Rigid Plastic Food Package Design</a><br /><i> Alvin S. Topolski and Douglas Reece</i></p> </div></div></div><div id="left">
